<h1>Future Prospects - Payment Received</h1>

<p>Hello <%= @student.full_name %>,</p>

<p>This email is to inform you that the following payment has been received:</p>

<ul>
  <li>Amount: <strong><%= number_to_currency @payment.amount_pounds, unit: 'Â£' %></strong></li>
  <li>Description: <strong><%= @payment.description %></strong></li>
  <li>Payment Type: <strong><%= @payment.payment_type %></strong></li>
  <li>Payment Date: <strong><%= format_date @payment.created_at %></strong></li>
  <% if @payment.credit_card? %>
    <li>Card Holder: <strong><%= @payment.card_holder %></strong></li>
    <li>Card Number: <strong><%= credit_card_number @payment.last_four_digits %></strong></li>
  <% end %>
</ul>

<p>This means that you application can now be processed and sent to your selected colleges for consideration. You will
be contacted when a decision has been made about a course you have applied for.</p>

<p>In order to track your application, please <%= link_to 'sign in', root_url %> to the Future Prospects site and use
  the track application option.</p>

<p>Sincerely,
  <br><br>
  Future Prospects</p>
